reviewText: The same is available on Utube.
thank you for a good part

This is what you want if you are going to buy an English wheel. I saw several videos on U tube that are good but this covers the basics better and makes on line stuff easy to understand. Well worth the price.
As a beginner this was really helpful and informative. I wish it was a little longer, but thats not to say I think anything was left out.
